<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>NGO Donation System</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #121212; color: #f0f0f0; text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; }
        h1 { color: #ff4d4d; font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 10px; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000; }
        p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .btn-container { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; }
        .btn { padding: 15px 40px; font-size: 1.2rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 30px; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; font-weight: bold; }
        .btn-login { background: transparent; border: 2px solid #ff4d4d; color: #ff4d4d; }
        .btn-login:hover { background: #ff4d4d; color: white; box-shadow: 0 0 15px #ff4d4d; }
        .btn-register { background: #ff4d4d; color: white; border: 2px solid #ff4d4d; }
        .btn-register:hover { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff4d4d; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>❤️ Hope & Care Foundation</h1>
    <p>Empowering lives through your generosity. Join us today.</p>
    
    <div class="btn-container">
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-login">Login</a>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-register">Start Donating</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>